```

## Hard Rules
- No implementation code in this phase.
- No refactoring suggestions unless directly required by the goal.
- No new dependencies unless justified — state why existing deps or the standard library cannot solve it.
- If a structural change is needed — describe it, get explicit agreement, then implement separately.
- Do not propose liveness or readiness endpoints unless they are part of the goal — but if the goal introduces a new core component, flag that it will need them (`team-rules/conventions.mdc`).
